Manual configuration
    * Chances of mis-configuration
    * Difficult to transfer the configuration knowledge to other team members

IAC
    * Automate creating updating and destroying cloud infra

SDLC of infra  
    * Plan design test deliver maintain and retire cloud infra

Reliabiltiy
    * Idempotent and predictable consistent infra

Configuration Drift
    * Changes that go unnoticed when performing infra automation
    * These configuration changes should be detected, corrected and prevented with tools like aws config ,bridgecrew ,etc
